      • addSubscriber

        public void addSubscriber(Subscriber s,
                          org.ntnunotif.wsnu.services.implementations.notificationproducer.AbstractNotificationProducer.SubscriptionHandle subHandle)
        This is the main OKSE implementation of the subscription manager addSubscriber method that should be used. It will delegate core subscriber registry to the core SubscriptionService, as well as update the local mappings from WS-Nu subscriptionKey to the relevant Subscriber and SubscriptionHandle objects.
        Parameters:
        s - An instance of OKSE Subscriber with proper fields and attributes set.
        subHandle - An instance of WS-Nu SubscriptionHandle with proper fields and attributes set.
